description:
This is a 2 minute workout called 'Prague Challenge Row' from the channel Mac Evans.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Competitor and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The The Competitor vibe means Gamified, leaderboard-driven, full-send energy. This is especially good for Those who need to chase a score or beat their own record. The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible..
The technique difficulty is Advanced.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Bolt towards the Czech Bridge with Mac in Prague as you exert maximum effort. 

Max rhythm: 32, Format: Power...
